    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Used to distinguish the variety of Spanish spoken in Spain, on the Iberian Peninsula, from other forms spoken elsewhere. To refer specifically to formal varieties of Spanish as spoken in Spain, use "Castilian Spanish."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
